只過了一秒鐘。Yeesa發現自己的穿越能力不由自主，而她竟然在現實裡重新認識Ryan及家聰&hellip;&hellip;命運的齒輪在靜靜地轉動著&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n導演及各演員們IG or YouTube<br />\n<br />\n導演 羅嘉駿 @stev.law <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/stevelawhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fstevelawhk&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=f5f92e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/stevelawhk</a><br />\n編劇 黃智揚 @yellow_wong_yellow<br />\n副導演兼 Alien - 鄭文熙 @manscheng<br />\n製作人兼 關羽 - 關永宇 @yukwanwing<br />\n演員:<br />\nYeesa - 吳海昕 Sofiee Ng @sofiee_ng <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/Sofieeyan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2FSofieeyan&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=aa1b085e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/Sofieeyan</a><br />\nRyan - 徐天佑 Chui Tien You @chuihammer<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=e72b2f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCi-u7xxaBviW9Ov1yL-5Bow</a><br />\n余家聰/會長 - 劉俊謙 Terrance Lau @lauchunhim.terrance<br />\n巴西龜 - 岑珈其 @kakisham<br />\nFiona - 李敏 @ranyayaya<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/yatotheworld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Fyatotheworld&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=c49e5717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/yatotheworld</a><br />\n嘉嘉 - 張凱娸 @kikicheungg<br />\nJonathan - 柯煒林 @willallwailam<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL65oFa-cpNMTjKfrnxg74w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCL65oFa-cpNMTjKfrnxg74w&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=700e154e\" data-auto-link target=\"_bl